She walked to her room and slammed the door behind her.
She paced back and forth across the room.
"My goodness.  Cybershark must now think me to be an idiot."  She 
fumed,"And that Grimmler,  oohhh, I let him get to me like that! I 
can't beleive I let that happen.  And of all the stupid things to 
say." She made her voice sound higher,"Yes we'll share quarters." her 
voice going back to normal, but aggitated,"Ooohh, of all the stupid, 
idiotic, unthinking..." she fumed as she paced around the room.
"I can't beleive I let him do that to me. And in front of CyberChark,"
She put her hand over her eyes and sighed,"Oh, he must think of me as 
nothing more than an overflustered female who can't handle 
anything."  She sighed and sat down in her chair.
